@bergmeister, GUIDs aren't necessary *most* times, and WiX recommends against them. I removed the GUIDs because, when the path changes ("7" vs. "7-preview"), having the same GUID ref-counts different files/registry values in different locations, thus leading to all sorts of problems.

But they are necessary when you don't have a single automatic key path, namely files, registry, and a couple others.

I'll take a look.
